						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying near the tank in the quarter called ‘Māyaguṇḍi’</p>						

						<p>Circa 15th Century.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Tāraṇa Vriśchika,</hi> other being lost. It mentions Puttūru and seems to register a gift of money to the <hi rend="italic">grāma-dēvaru.</hi></p>						

